  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Power Management Utilities</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Power Management Utilities</application> is a small
      collection of scripts to suspend et hibernate computer that can be used
      to run user supplied scripts on suspend et resume.
    </para>

    &lfs73_checked;

